nodes.text: Dasha Sigweed was a Twi'lek singer and DJ living during the Clone Wars. He was known for his loud, rhythmic leap-jump style.

Dasha Sigweed's name is a play on the name of the European DJ duo Sasha & John Digweed. In Slugthrowers: An Overview of Popular Music and Musicians in a Galaxy Far, Far Away, a 2013 article written by Edward M. Erdelac for the official StarWars.com blog, the character was mistakenly referred to as "Sasha Digweed."
